title: Ukase T1 - T4 (2007) (Sosich & V2) cbr
description:
Sirweed Galver, number 2 of CIA undercover department, is close to retirement. He is ready to take a well deserved rest after years of dangerous missions, and hopes to find peace after the death of his wife. This February was intended to oversee the end of an infiltration of the Russian mafia. The aim is to seize the Siberian oil assets. Code Name: BLACK STORM.
